solution:
Since the graph of $y = \sin (3x - \pi)$ is the same as the graph of $y = \sin 3x$ shifted $\frac{\pi}{3}$ units to the right, the phase shift is $\boxed{\frac{\pi}{3}}.$

[asy]import TrigMacros;

